(Noel Gallagher)</a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">不会参加巡演</a>，但这位创作歌手兼吉他手本周早些时候确实宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-announce-summer-2024-uk-shows-3553168">High Flying Birds 将于 2024 年夏季在英国进行一系列演出</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/anyway-heres-wonderwall-covered-by-mr-blobby-3556236">无论如何，这里是“Wonderwall”——由 Blobby 先生翻唱的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
